OL,3,CRob Elliot: new Carlisle United boss
OL,4,Cplans 'to get the place rocking'
OL,6,FNew Carlisle United boss Rob Elliot
OL,7,Fsaid he wants fans to enjoy
OL,8,F"aggressive, attacking football" as he
OL,9,Fset out his stall in his first
OL,10,Finterviews since taking charge of the
OL,11,FBlues.
OL,13,FThe former Newcastle United goalkeeper
OL,14,Fjoined days after leaving Gateshead
OL,15,Ffollowing a second successful spell at
OL,16,Fthe National League side which saw him
OL,17,Fpull the club from the bottom of the
OL,18,Ftable to safety.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/10
