CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1780337465
OL,3,CRob Elliot: new Carlisle United boss
OL,4,Cplans 'to get the place rocking'
OL,6,FThe new Head Coach has replaced Mark
OL,7,FHughes, who left Carlisle by mutual
OL,8,Fconsent after failing to get promoted
OL,9,Fback to the Football League through
OL,10,Fthe playoffs.
OL,12,FSpeaking to ITV News Border, Elliot
OL,13,Fsaid: "My pledge is that we want to
OL,14,Fplay great football, we want the club
OL,15,Fto be successful, but I think the most
OL,16,Fimportant thing is we put a team out
OL,17,Fthat gives absolutely everything for
OL,18,Fthe badge.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/10
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,353,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1780337465
OL,3,CRob Elliot: new Carlisle United boss
OL,4,Cplans 'to get the place rocking'
OL,6,F"You get 10,000-plus (supporters) at
OL,7,Fhome games; it's a fantastically
OL,8,Fsupported club, and we want to give
OL,9,Fthem something to be excited about,
OL,10,Fget the place rocking and look forward
OL,11,Fto some good times.
OL,13,F"We want to play aggressive, attacking
OL,14,Ffootball, and we want to make sure
OL,15,Fwe're aggressive without the ball, we
OL,16,Fwant to win it back as quick as
OL,17,Fpossible, defend high up the pitch.
OL,26,@nD@VpmnD@apn
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/10
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,353,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1780337465
OL,3,CRob Elliot: new Carlisle United boss
OL,4,Cplans 'to get the place rocking'
OL,6,FElliot praised the commitment of fans
OL,7,Fwho have seen their club relegated
OL,8,Ftwice in recent years, dropping from
OL,9,FLeague One in 2023 to the fifth tier
OL,10,Fof english football in 2025.
OL,12,FHe said: "Thank you for the welcome,
OL,13,Fit's been brilliant, just keep doing
OL,14,Fwhat (you've) been doing, supporting
OL,15,Fthe team.
OL,17,F"They've done it incredibly
OL,18,Fconsidering the last few years with
OL,19,Fthe relegations, and I think now we
OL,20,Fwant to turn that chapter and start a
OL,21,Fnew era of positivity."
OL,26,@vD@FpmvD@Mpn
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/10
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
