FL,353,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1780337465
OL,3,CRob Elliot: new Carlisle United boss
OL,4,Cplans 'to get the place rocking'
OL,6,FElliot promised the club will
OL,7,F"definitely" be making singings, and
OL,8,Fsaid he will be involved in
OL,9,Frecruitment.
OL,11,FHe said: "Meeting the owners, they've
OL,12,Fbeen really supportive, they obviously
OL,13,Fcare a lot about the club, and put a
OL,14,Flot of time and effort into improving
OL,15,Fthe club off the pitch.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/10
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,353,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1780337465
OL,3,CRob Elliot: new Carlisle United boss
OL,4,Cplans 'to get the place rocking'
OL,6,F"On the pitch it obviously hasn't gone
OL,7,Fthe way everyone would have wanted the
OL,8,Flast few years but I think it's
OL,9,Fgetting to the point where the club's
OL,10,Fin a good place, it seems to run
OL,11,Fsmoothly, so it gives me an
OL,12,Fopportunity to concentrate on the
OL,13,Ffootball."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G6/10
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,353,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1780337465
OL,3,CRob Elliot: new Carlisle United boss
OL,4,Cplans 'to get the place rocking'
OL,6,F"Obviously it's a big club, with a
OL,7,Fgreat fanbase, but when you see the
OL,8,Fclub run, how many people it takes to
OL,9,Fkeep the club running and you see all
OL,10,Fthe community and the operational side
OL,11,Fand everything that goes into
OL,12,Fproducing what we see on a match day,
OL,13,Fit just shows what a big club we are
OL,14,Fand how well supported we are."
OL,16,FWho is Rob Elliot?
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G7/10
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
