CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1780337465
OL,3,CRob Elliot: new Carlisle United boss
OL,4,Cplans 'to get the place rocking'
OL,6,FLondon-born, Elliot played for
OL,7,FCharlton, Bishop's Stortford, Notts
OL,8,FCounty, Accrington Stanley and
OL,9,FNewcastle United and earned four caps
OL,10,Fwith the Republic of Ireland.
OL,12,FHis managerial career started at
OL,13,FGateshead as caretaker manager,
OL,14,Fleading the team to a sixth-placed
OL,15,Ffinish in the National League and the
OL,16,Fclub's first FA Trophy victory in 2024.
OL,18,FHe was then appointed permanent
OL,19,Fmanager, before moving to League One
OL,20,Fside Crawley Town in October 2024.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G8/10
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,353,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1780337465
OL,3,CRob Elliot: new Carlisle United boss
OL,4,Cplans 'to get the place rocking'
OL,6,FElliot was sacked in March 2025 with
OL,7,Fthe club 12 points from safety.
OL,9,FIn January 2026 he returned to
OL,10,FGateshead when they were bottom of the
OL,11,FNational League, but turned around the
OL,12,Fclub's fortunes to lead them to
OL,13,Fsafety, eventually finishing 18th.
OL,15,FAt the end of the season he left
OL,16,FGateshead, saying the club were unable
OL,17,Fto provide the budget and
OL,18,Finfrastructure he wanted to make
OL,19,Ffurther improvements.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G9/10
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
